{"tid":33974,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉心悠真係好正 可惜脫晒毛","createTime":"2016-12-11T07:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T16:13:26.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a04b407738a37effef3ff9a97ada7ef6db9108f","tid":33974,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"J唔落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mxiii.cms.ccue.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/20140722_%E5%8A%89%E5%BF%83%E6%82%A0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmxiii.cms.ccue.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F07%2F20140722_%25E5%258A%2589%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2582%25A0.jpg&h=bd0dc542&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08ee310c9ab4d0fc4dc5e1cfce8ac0ebdb3f0653","tid":33974,"uid":63258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:43:44.000Z","msg":"你又知脫晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867644e8184ad1cae14b0517cd6e4cf8c71a7168","tid":33974,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:52:28.000Z","msg":"眉毛呢"},{"pid":"d67276f7ea73148f236a5ef0d8ab9539f24dc046","tid":33974,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:58:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你又知脫晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n劉心悠為激光脫毛中心擔任代言人，在拍攝平面廣告當天，由於攝影室又濕又冷，而且經過18小時長時間拍攝，肌膚白滑無瑕的劉心悠，凍得她全身麻痺起來，她說：「5年前已經開始接受全身激光脫毛療程，效果唔錯。」劉心悠表示，由於studio實在太凍，所以在休息時間，她立刻披上一件紅色有帽子的波點毛毛外套，工作人員都說她可愛得像「小紅帽」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.am730.com.hk/article-64301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Farticle-64301&d=rciifYXlWV7fycG9tPDU5AT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=87e19247\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.am730.com.hk/article-64301</a>"},{"pid":"e8a1a8efb47a0c0c8575df6bc03f949a02d537ea","tid":33974,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"